{"tid":2359903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天水圍居屋都有移民盤 綠表業主440萬沽貨走人 帳面賺逾300萬","createTime":"2021-01-09T09:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T09:16:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7252157e3a344eb4df198663da5e28ccbdd2edc2","tid":2359903,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"祥益地產高級區域經理黃肇雯表示，天水圍居屋天頌苑錄區內首置客成交，原業主於2001年以95.9萬購入單位，是次轉手帳面獲利344.1萬，單位升值逾3倍易手。據了解業主於上年10月放盤原本叫價500萬，由於已移民離港，故增加議幅累積減價達60萬，買家決定以440萬(居二市場價)購入上址作自住用，實用面積呎價6769元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2847979/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%9B%A4%C2%A0%E7%B6%A0%E8%A1%A8%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB440%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E8%B2%A8%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%BA%C2%A0%E5%B8%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%BA%E9%80%BE300%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2847979%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259B%25A4%25C2%25A0%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB440%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25C2%25A0%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E9%2580%25BE300%25E8%2590%25AC&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=100442fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2847979/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%9B%A4%C2%A0%E7%B6%A0%E8%A1%A8%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB440%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E8%B2%A8%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%BA%C2%A0%E5%B8%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%BA%E9%80%BE300%E8%90%AC</a>"}]}